            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">安布西洛·R/阿拉米</span></div></div></div><p>海洋边界的建立是为了恢复蓝鳍金枪鱼的数量，将大西洋划分为截然不同的捕鱼区。<em>理查德·亚当斯·凯里的评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/kings-of-their-own-ocean-review-the-trouble-with-tuna-97c98c24?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
